should be celebrated.

00:31:10.433 --> 00:31:13.400
Which is why I would like
to give a shout out

00:31:13.400 --> 00:31:15.967
to someone very special...

00:31:15.967 --> 00:31:17.133
Cole.

00:31:17.967 --> 00:31:22.300
Thank you so much for always
believing in me,

00:31:22.300 --> 00:31:24.633
for empowering me,

00:31:24.633 --> 00:31:28.600
and for helping me be the best
version of myself.

00:31:30.400 --> 00:31:33.233
Everyone, please give him
a round of applause.

00:31:33.233 --> 00:31:40.200
