00:32:52.433 --> 00:32:53.467
What's wrong?

00:32:54.500 --> 00:32:55.567
Tell me.

00:32:56.667 --> 00:32:58.067
Now!

00:32:58.067 --> 00:32:59.667
I was surprised you
ranked second.

00:33:01.133 --> 00:33:02.167
Me too!

00:33:04.000 --> 00:33:05.000
Finally...

00:33:06.200 --> 00:33:08.133
Finally someone agrees
with me.

00:33:08.967 --> 00:33:10.967
I thought I was going to be
number one this time,

00:33:10.967 --> 00:33:13.333
but that girlfriend of yours
is just lucky

00:33:13.333 --> 00:33:15.367
that she has
a photographic memory.

00:33:15.367 --> 00:33:18.000
But did she actually understand
what she was reading?

00:33:19.233 --> 00:33:20.333
But wait...

00:33:21.500 --> 00:33:23.933
What does my rank
have to do with this?

00:33:27.700 --> 00:33:29.167
Are you jealous?

00:33:29.167 --> 00:33:30.033
[SCOFFS]

00:33:30.033 --> 00:33:32.133
Then you should've
studied harder.

00:33:32.733 --> 00:33:34.633
Or you should've hired
a tutor.

00:33:35.633 --> 00:33:36.600
[THUD]

00:33:36.600 --> 00:33:41.067
[COLE BREATHING HEAVILY]

00:33:41.067 --> 00:33:42.333
You're angry...

00:33:43.367 --> 00:33:46.233
because two of your girlfriends
outsmarted you.

00:33:49.233 --> 00:33:50.700
Did I hurt your ego?

00:33:50.700 --> 00:33:54.400
[UNSETTLING MUSIC PLAYING]

00:33:54.400 --> 00:33:55.533
Isobel...

00:33:56.267 --> 00:33:59.533
I don't owe you
or anyone an explanation.

00:34:01.300 --> 00:34:03.367
I don't give a damn
about your ranking.

00:34:04.767 --> 00:34:07.600
Because even if you turn
the world upside down...

00:34:12.400 --> 00:34:15.133
you'll never be
my number one.

00:34:15.133 --> 00:34:16.167
- [COLE GRUNTS]
- [SLAMS LOCKER]

00:34:16.167 --> 00:34:18.667
[COLE BREATHING HEAVILY]

00:34:18.667 --> 00:34:22.033
[UNSETTLING MUSIC CONTINUES]

00:34:22.033 --> 00:34:23.533
You're never going to break up
