I begged you, remember?

00:36:38.833 --> 00:36:41.633
Marla, this is the first time
I asked a favor from you, right?

00:36:42.400 --> 00:36:45.533
Is it hard to make
a few mistakes on our exams?

00:36:46.633 --> 00:36:49.533
It's not as if I asked you
to get a failing grade.

00:36:49.533 --> 00:36:52.900
I was just asking for
a little consideration,

00:36:52.900 --> 00:36:55.633
so I could be the top in our
class even just this quarter.

00:36:55.633 --> 00:36:58.233
Just one quarter! So that my dad
won't get mad at me!

00:36:58.233 --> 00:36:59.867
You know how he's like, right?

00:37:02.500 --> 00:37:03.833
- But...
- What?

00:37:08.967 --> 00:37:10.833
Cole, it's just that...

00:37:12.200 --> 00:37:16.167
even if I got some of the
answers wrong,

00:37:17.300 --> 00:37:19.900
you still wouldn't be
the top in our class.

00:37:20.867 --> 00:37:23.300
So, you're saying
that I'm dumb?

00:37:24.333 --> 00:37:26.333
- No. No.
- Is that what you're implying?

00:37:26.333 --> 00:37:28.233
- No. It's not that.
- Is that it?

00:37:28.233 --> 00:37:29.600
Then what?!

00:37:29.600 --> 00:37:32.567
Hey. Hey.

00:37:32.567 --> 00:37:35.333
You're a SOSH student.

00:37:35.333 --> 00:37:37.433
No one here is dumb.

00:37:37.433 --> 00:37:40.367
And no one is calling
