00:37:40.367 --> 00:37:43.700
But I admit I was scared
to give up my rank

00:37:43.700 --> 00:37:45.633
because I have goals, too.

00:37:46.333 --> 00:37:49.833
I want to graduate on top and
get a scholarship in Harvard.

00:37:51.367 --> 00:37:53.600
We all have dreams, don't we?

00:37:53.600 --> 00:37:56.667
Yes, we have dreams.

00:37:56.667 --> 00:37:59.800
But why did you agree
to give way for me, Marla?

00:37:59.800 --> 00:38:01.967
