are all women?

00:38:08.367 --> 00:38:09.767
There's nothing wrong with that.

00:38:09.767 --> 00:38:11.633
You don't understand, Marla,

00:38:11.633 --> 00:38:14.033
because you already got
what you want.

00:38:14.033 --> 00:38:15.733
I thought you loved me.

00:38:16.867 --> 00:38:17.867
I do.

00:38:17.867 --> 00:38:20.800
But your grades
are more important to you.

00:38:22.400 --> 00:38:23.367
No.

00:38:24.633 --> 00:38:27.600
Cole, I love you.

00:38:27.600 --> 00:38:30.500
But you couldn't give way
for me.

00:38:30.500 --> 00:38:32.933
You know I'm applying for
an internship at NASA, right?

00:38:32.933 --> 00:38:34.633
My future depends on that!

00:38:35.833 --> 00:38:38.633
You know that they'll only get
the top student

00:38:38.633 --> 00:38:41.867
