00:39:07.400 --> 00:39:09.000
So, what do you want me
to do?

00:39:09.800 --> 00:39:11.600
Should I just blame myself?

00:39:11.600 --> 00:39:13.633
Am I the one
at fault here, Marla?

00:39:13.633 --> 00:39:16.333
When I get home,
Daddy would kill me.

00:39:16.333 --> 00:39:18.700
I don't know how
you could make it up to me,

00:39:18.700 --> 00:39:20.767
